00:08:38,920 --> 00:08:44,440
Now this is a standalone alkyne, there's only one kind like it itself, and that's because

104
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:49,920
acetylene has hydrogens attached, remember chain terminating hydrogens, attached to both

105
00:08:49,920 --> 00:08:53,640
of the carbons involved in the triple bond.

